### 6. 3NF Example

❌ Before 3NF

| EmpID | EmpName | DeptID | DeptName |
| ----- | ------- | ------ | -------- |
| 1     | Arun    | D1     | HR       |

`DeptName` depends on `DeptID`, not directly on `EmpID`.

✅ After 3NF

**Employees**

| EmpID | EmpName | DeptID |
| ----- | ------- | ------ |
| 1     | Arun    | D1     |

**Departments**

| DeptID | DeptName |
| ------ | -------- |
| D1     | HR       |
